Title: QRPs in the Publish-or-Perish Culture
Description: This study examines the effects of publication pressure on the use of questionable research practices (QRPs) in psychological science.
Contributors: Bennett Kleinberg, Yoram Kevin Kunkels, Vincent de Haan
Tags: 

QRPs in the Publish-or-Perish Culture
This study examines the effects of publication pressure on the use of questionable research practices (QRPs) in psychological science.
